ezvcard.property

Class OrgDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ezvcard.property.VCardProperty
      • ezvcard.property.SimpleProperty<String>
        • ezvcard.property.TextProperty
          • ezvcard.property.UriProperty
            • ezvcard.property.OrgDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasAltId, Comparable<VCardProperty>

    public class OrgDirectory
extends UriProperty
implements HasAltId

    Defines a URI that can be used to retrieve information about the person's co-workers.

    Code sample 

     VCard vcard = new VCard();
 
 OrgDirectory orgDirectory = new OrgDirectory("http://www.company.com/staff");
 vcard.addOrgDirectory(orgDirectory);

    Property name: ORG-DIRECTORY

    Supported versions: 4.0

    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 6715
